5.1 The Problem We're Solving

Imagine one compromised agent could:

Â· Drain your OpenAI credits
Â· Delete production databases
Â· Send spam to customers
Â· Exfiltrate sensitive data

Traditional security fails because agents need some access to do their jobs.

