6.3 The Logging Philosophy

Three types of logs for three different audiences:

1. Operational Logs (For SREs)
   Â· Machine parseable
   Â· High volume
   Â· System health focused
2. Audit Logs (For compliance)
   Â· Immutable
   Â· Complete trail
   Â· Security focused
3. Debug Logs (For developers)
   Â· Human readable
   Â· Context rich
   Â· Problem solving focused

AES adds a fourth:

1. Ethical Logs (For ethics review)
   Â· Decision rationales
   Â· Alternative options considered
   Â· Impact assessments

