7.2 Certification Requirements Matrix

Requirement Bronze Silver Gold
Compliance Basic AES interface Full interface + error handling All + ACP protocol
Security No dangerous patterns Security audit + token scoping Penetration tested
Performance Functional <1s average latency <0.5s latency, 99.9% uptime
Stability 24-hour run 30-day production 6-month production
Documentation API docs Full docs + tutorials Docs + case studies
Testing Unit tests Integration tests Load tests + chaos engineering
Observability Basic logs Full monitoring Real-time dashboard
Interoperability Self-contained Works with 2+ other agents Works in multi-agent ecosystem

