The Call to Action

This isn't just another open source project. This is:

1. A Movement - For open, interoperable AI
2. A Foundation - For the agent economy
3. A Safeguard - Against AI fragmentation
4. An Opportunity - To shape the future of AI

We have two paths forward:

Path A (Without AES):

Â· Every company builds proprietary systems
Â· Agents can't talk to each other
Â· Vendor lock-in strangles innovation
Â· AI progress fragments and slows
Â· We repeat the mistakes of the early Internet

Path B (With AES):

Â· Open standard enables interoperability
Â· Agents collaborate across boundaries
Â· Innovation accelerates dramatically
Â· Small teams can build what only giants can today
Â· We create a rising tide that lifts all boats

The choice is obvious. The time is now.

